01:56.360 --> 02:02.000
And now to other matters, as a member of the Interior Subcommittee of the Appropriations Committee,

02:02.000 --> 02:07.760
I had the privilege this week of urging on behalf of Senator Gore and myself an additional

02:07.760 --> 02:14.360
$240,000 to provide 200 more campsites in the Smoky Mountain National Park.

02:14.360 --> 02:19.960
I also did this on behalf of the Smoky Mountain National Park Commission and Herbides

02:19.960 --> 02:23.000
Walters of Maristown, its chairman.

02:23.000 --> 02:28.800
Conrad Worth, the Director of the National Park Service, backed this request wholeheartedly.

02:28.800 --> 02:32.480
