16:18.200 --> 16:25.640
have addressed in the past month in Tennessee. And as a matter of fact, I also had the privilege of

16:25.640 --> 16:32.680
delivering the graduating address when my daughter Linda graduated here in high school in Washington.

16:33.640 --> 16:40.760
And I just thought as I saw all of these wonderful children graduating in high schools in Tennessee,

16:41.800 --> 16:47.800
what a great thing it would be if we could see to it that they all had opportunities in business and

16:47.800 --> 16:56.680
farming and industry in the volunteer state and not have to send them out of the some other state

16:56.680 --> 17:03.320
to have an opportunity. This is incidentally as a great challenge to us grown-ups to do everything

17:03.320 --> 17:08.840
we can to see that this is possible. Rather than the faces and the words of these young people,

17:08.840 --> 17:16.280
I have seen only confidence and a determination to conquer the economic, social, and political and

17:16.280 --> 17:23.560
cultural challenges of a most difficult era. If there is anything I can tell you that may help

17:23.560 --> 17:31.320
