18:04.840 --> 18:12.680
may be of value, but you are the one who will live with your life. Design it for happiness and

18:12.680 --> 18:21.160
around the contribution you can make to society and to your fellow men. Make no place for cynics or

18:21.160 --> 18:27.320
profits of doom. They will tell you that the splitting of the atom has made your world a mockery,

18:27.880 --> 18:35.000
that your efforts for peace and mankind are in vain. Health faith in yourself, in your people,

18:35.000 --> 18:42.360
and in your country. This is your time in history. You can make it or break it. And with it all,

